OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"But there's two things that keep me
OL,8,Fgoing really, I can do more things
OL,9,Ftoday than I could do yesterday, so
OL,10,FI'll be able to do more tomorrow. And,
OL,11,Fyou've got to say well it's better
OL,12,Fthan the alternative, and I was very
OL,13,Fclose to the alternative, which was
OL,14,Fdeath."
OL,16,FOn an episode of a podcast called The
OL,17,FSepsis Voices with Dr Ron, Lord
OL,18,FMackinlay described himself as a
OL,19,F"bionic Lord" due to his prosthetics.
