OL,7,FHe has pledged to "battle" with the
OL,8,FHealth Secretary on working to ensure
OL,9,Famputees receive adequate prosthetic
OL,10,Flimbs, condemning a "postcode lottery"
OL,11,Fsystem currently faced by those
OL,12,Frelying on the NHS.
OL,14,FHe said: "The NHS work off a list:
OL,15,Fyear one you'll have these rubber,
OL,16,Fblunt instruments. Year two, they
OL,17,Fmight give you a body-powered thing
OL,18,Fthat looks like something out of
OL,19,FVictorian times.
