OL,4,CLords, vowing to fight for sepsis
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FLord Mackinlay added he wants to see a
OL,8,Fsepsis campaign mirroring the NHS's
OL,9,FAct FAST, which has raised awareness
OL,10,Ffor stroke symptoms.
OL,12,FHe said: He added: "The trouble is
OL,13,Fthere's not really a one size fits all
OL,14,Fmenu, not really, but to try and get
OL,15,Fan awareness early, because sepsis
OL,16,Fkills 48,000 people a year, it's a
OL,17,Fhuge killer in the UK.
OL,19,F"We devote a lot of time to looking at
OL,20,Fother diseases, but not quite the same
OL,21,Fto this mass killer."
